06:05.815 --> 06:07.383
So I was looking at my speech

06:07.384 --> 06:08.938
from last year's women's conference,

06:08.939 --> 06:10.153
you know, checking for ideas...

06:10.154 --> 06:12.577
And by "checking for ideas,"
you mean you hope to reuse

06:12.578 --> 06:13.745
last year's speech.

06:13.746 --> 06:15.180
No.

06:15.181 --> 06:17.949
Well, I don't want to say
that parts of it are timeless,

06:17.950 --> 06:20.518
but that would not
be totally inaccurate.

06:20.519 --> 06:22.887
Except the demographics have changed.

06:22.888 --> 06:25.557
We have a 20% uptick in
attendance in women under 30,

06:25.558 --> 06:28.727
who seem to think equal pay
for equal work is a fine idea.

06:28.728 --> 06:31.329
Man, I'm glad you're back.

06:31.330 --> 06:33.865
Okay, let's just spitball these ideas,

06:33.866 --> 06:35.300
and we'll write my speech.

06:35.301 --> 06:36.416
Help you?

06:36.417 --> 06:38.735
I have a press briefing to
give, e-mails to catch up on,

06:38.736 --> 06:40.505
and breasts to pump.
How about you help me?

06:40.506 --> 06:42.574
Okay.

06:42.575 --> 06:44.309
Just so you know, I'm leaving because

06:44.310 --> 06:45.844
you want to get rid of me,

06:45.845 --> 06:48.046
not because I'm afraid
of breast-pumping.

06:48.047 --> 06:49.781
Whatever works.

06:49.782 --> 06:52.583
Just a friend thing.

06:54.319 --> 06:56.354
How are your parents handling this?

06:56.355 --> 07:00.158
It's gonna take some time,
but they'll come around.

07:00.159 --> 07:02.694
Well, if you're looking
for some extended family,

07:02.695 --> 07:04.029
I'd like to offer up mine.

07:04.030 --> 07:07.232
As you know, I'm half
Irish, half Pakistani,

07:07.233 --> 07:10.468
so it's a lot of whiplash
in the lifestyle department.

07:10.469 --> 07:12.771
You got drinkers and teetotalers,

07:12.772 --> 07:14.706
carnivores, vegetarians,

07:14.707 --> 07:17.242
shouters and... well, everybody shouts.

07:17.243 --> 07:18.777
But in a fun way.

07:18.778 --> 07:20.778
And they all love babies.

07:21.713 --> 07:23.848
Okay, I wanted to strangle you

07:23.849 --> 07:25.417
a minute ago,

07:25.418 --> 07:28.353
now I feel all weepy.

07:28.354 --> 07:29.854
Damn hormones.

07:29.855 --> 07:33.425
Think about it. Open invitation.

07:33.426 --> 07:36.059
Everybody needs family.

