11:09.015 --> 11:10.584
You okay?

11:10.585 --> 11:13.420
I was just thinking...

11:13.421 --> 11:16.523
if I had never gone to War College or...

11:16.524 --> 11:19.326
or met you, if I had stayed
in the Russian military

11:19.327 --> 11:22.062
and been a good soldier...

11:22.063 --> 11:23.797
then this is where I'd be now.

11:23.798 --> 11:26.066
Helping to prop up an armed insurgency

11:26.067 --> 11:28.568
and destabilize the elected government.

11:28.569 --> 11:30.070
Let's just hope that Matvey Sokolov

11:30.071 --> 11:32.539
is as cynical as you are
about Russia's intentions here.

11:32.540 --> 11:36.543
I have faith Matvey has
remained an idealist.

11:36.544 --> 11:40.979
And if not, then, yeah, I'm
sure he still loves money.

11:57.864 --> 11:59.065
Daisy!

11:59.066 --> 12:01.701
Mrs. Garcia.

12:01.702 --> 12:04.470
Oh, please, call me Margarita.

12:05.538 --> 12:08.408
Oh, my God.

12:08.409 --> 12:11.177
She looks just like him.

12:11.178 --> 12:12.979
Yes, you know that?

12:12.980 --> 12:14.481
You look like your daddy.

12:15.650 --> 12:18.650
Oh, I'm so happy to
meet you. Come on in.

12:22.956 --> 12:25.058
Dr. McCord, I was told

12:25.059 --> 12:26.626
you would be coming alone.

12:26.627 --> 12:29.094
I brought an old friend to see you.

12:32.032 --> 12:33.816
Dim?

